name: OpenWebUi
description: User-friendly AI Interface (Supports Ollama, OpenAI API, ...)
info:
Useful to test LLMs in your pool with a neat playground GUI.
Does not require GPUs
template_rules: Playground is a GUI interface for models, but does not itself deploy any models. With the OpenWebUi template you can deploy a full browser based UI playground to test your LLM models in your cluster.
